{"tid":411621,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"去一次海洋公園就見盡人生百態...去一次海洋公園就見盡人生百態...","createTime":"2017-09-24T03:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T05:53:37.000Z","uid":4806,"like":51,"dislike":89,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b1899a815de2192a4660595bd8bb708a93deb3a","tid":411621,"uid":4806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:51:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今日同成班巴打去OP玩<br />\n另外仲有幾個女仔frd搭frd一齊<br />\nOk啦咁識下朋友無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n約左係金鐘等<br />\n其中一個巴打(下稱A)就遲大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地喺地鐵月台等佢啦<br />\n佢就臨上車先出現<br />\n仲遲過d女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌 都算<br />\n<br />\n入到去 A同d女仔未買飛<br />\n咁我地成班買哂飛就係隔離等佢地<br />\n等左半粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢就排隊買隊溝女<br />\n我地就同門口d大媽曬太陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌 都算<br />\n<br />\n之後排排下鬼屋落大雨<br />\n成班人得我一個有帶遮<br />\nA就拎左我把遮去遮d女仔<br />\n我地就地圖當遮 濕撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要問我做咩唔帶多把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌 都算<br />\n<br />\n我地成班得A有拎袋<br />\n佢就話自己有d唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咁叫我地幫佢拎<br />\n屌 都算<br />\n<br />\n之後又有個鬼屋要排勁撚耐<br />\nA就提議同d女仔去玩海盜船<br />\n玩完同我地輪流排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我地就黎到個陣佢先出返黎<br />\n排左成粒鐘呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢就有得同班女玩海盜船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌 都算<br />\n<br />\n仲有我買左魚蛋燒賣<br />\n諗住大家一齊食都無所謂啦<br />\n點知A拎左d野食俾d女仔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌 都算<br />\n<br />\n最後諗住我地班巴打一齊坐一部纜車<br />\n點知佢話唔想咁迫<br />\n自己一個同d女坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地班仔就自己坐<br />\n屌 都算<br />\n<br />\n臨走A仲要話自己全日無洗過錢<br />\n（因為佢有得買免費飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ）<br />\n潤鳩我地<br />\n我地就俾幾舊水入去排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢就人生贏家<br />\n我地毒撚就幫佢排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c87ed8628e4afb90c5b0a0910a18b0ba5ddcad2d","tid":411621,"uid":2419,"like":221,"dislike":3,"score":218,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:53:25.000Z","msg":"你全程都唔出聲咁廢?"},{"pid":"8b544b16b98b5a952ab5b69409f3ba5aec27412d","tid":411621,"uid":44243,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:53:27.000Z","msg":"@新會然"},{"pid":"24e38b2c3619e747f04d57ee782125ff8db425df","tid":411621,"uid":148611,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:53:51.000Z","msg":"無膽話佢， 抵你做毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7d5bff0333e3c2a95e1adefb30ba406dd5478c","tid":411621,"uid":88218,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:56:46.000Z","msg":"人地可能有埋下半場添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d89ee00d3d8c6c1f59508646f0df4dd10b7a85","tid":411621,"uid":88592,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:57:38.000Z","msg":"篇文咁熟口面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbdb4e61851d50c2a7fb0cba3716515b006b8a0a","tid":411621,"uid":25741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:57:44.000Z","msg":"辣殺"},{"pid":"94e507780dcd6055209282675d69c95b8540b8fe","tid":411621,"uid":25713,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:58:05.000Z","msg":"樓主毒撚 唔抵得人哋有女溝 上來攞安慰感"},{"pid":"c1de1a8574efd8b339e2489ab8890d93e6bb5385","tid":411621,"uid":88592,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:59:52.000Z","msg":"Post條友出黎啦，狗公咁仆街"},{"pi